ee    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwjbkoKdt-uTAxUUh4oHHZXhJ9hIpq6LrfC0uPRyygEEVl2Yww==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbDRtQzlBOHZUM0s5SlItTGxIYWtkNHZPMDBrd3xBQ3Jtc0ttQXBQa2djLUk1SDhxa2pPQUVBS0QtSmk3eFFzcVJGdXotbWNtMXlmaEpTQVBQMXJJdEtkLWNVQThycnVrMzVJaThyRVA1ako3YkpPRHdvS3pJQ3N1NklncTd1bGJHX1o4MzVFTFhSakJzcWlCM19mSQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=cujhpwWi1yY","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbDRtQzlBOHZUM0s5SlItTGxIYWtkNHZPMDBrd3xBQ3Jtc0ttQXBQa2djLUk1SDhxa2pPQUVBS0QtSmk3eFFzcVJGdXotbWNtMXlmaEpTQVBQMXJJdEtkLWNVQThycnVrMzVJaThyRVA1ako3YkpPRHdvS3pJQ3N1NklncTd1bGJHX1o4MzVFTFhSakJzcWlCM19mSQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=cujhpwWi1yY","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwjbkoKdt-uTAxUUh4oHHZXhJ9hIpq6LrfC0uPRyygEEVl2Yww==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbU1VTUkwWHlzcEJtUDQ0LVhPWjd1MDhrU2c5QXxBQ3Jtc0tsQ2x4U2xLVmdiVFdHZW5BaVJja0FheE5vd0VaNm0xdUlrRncycEplU202amxEZ1doZW9WSDRVa25aV2wwbGlaQkFhNEV5N21DTmdCb3p1Q3VkUzFpeTM1LWVQLThMR3VONnJ5QXd2aVhWN0JYRXNXVQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paypal.com%2Fcgi-bin%2Fwebscr%3Fcmd%3D_s-xclick%26hosted_button_id%3D64QMBRBXQSV6G\u0026v=cujhpwWi1yY","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbU1VTUkwWHlzc